msgstr ""

#: ../../source/feature/optical_bands.rst:264
msgid ""
"**Description**: Combines multiple SWIR bands to enhance the detection "
"and differentiation of built-up areas."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/feature/optical_bands.rst:265
msgid ""
"**Usage**: Employed in urban and regional planning to delineate built-up "
"from natural areas."
msgstr ""

